snippet.title: Johnny Depp Wins Legal Battle involving Amber Heard Donation
snippet.description:
In this video made by Ross Celebs we talk about Johnny Depp's victory in his legal case against his ex-wife Amber Heard. The American Civil Liberties Union and Children’s Hospital Los Angeles rejected that Amber Heard had donated the money. 

Fans of the Pirates of the Caribbean star have been vocal about that move for a while. Depp’s attorney Benjamin Chew told USA Today, “Mr. Depp is most gratified by the Court’s decision.” This is just another part of what is a long legal battle between the two actors.
#JohnnyDeppAmber #AmberheardDonation
